What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Technology is changing increasingly rapidly today, and there are a lot of tools for people to learn and use to get what they want.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Knowledge can help people understand what is happening, how they will benefit, and why they should use certain tools to get the desired things.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I learned the basics of programming, like HTML and Python, which I have been able to write codes that I use to help me get answers for many

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I spend a lot of time in front of a computer screen at work, and I wanted to reduce my manual tasks to free up my time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was able to write a tool that imports Excel spreadsheets and builds SQL databases based on the table structure.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I then run data queries against those databases to get the results I want, and it has saved me a lot of time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In addition, I was selected from my company to participate in its Intrapreneurship program, working on software for small businesses.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: has driven me to continue exploring the technology field.
